extendedInfo.description: Are you registered to attend Sport Events Congress 2013 hosted by the Canadian Sport Tourism Alliance from April 8th to 10th, 2013? This is Canada's largest annual gathering of sport, tourism professionals and event management firms. Join us for networking, topical sessions and seminars and the annual PRESTIGE Awards. For more information, visit www.canadiansporttourism.com.Keywords: CSTA, Canadian Sport Tourism Alliance, Sport, Tourism, SEC
